
# Load %WL and %WLen
sub SetWLHash {
    my($rWL, $rWLen) = @_;  my($w, $wlen, @W);  
    local $/; $/ = "\n";
    while (<DATA>) { # load %WLen first
    	chomp;  	last if /^__END_OF_WLen__$/;
    	($w, $wlen) = split / : /, $_;
    	$rWLen->{$w} = $wlen;
    }
    while (<DATA>) { # load %WL
    	chomp; 	@W = split /\t/, $_;
    	foreach $w (@W) { $rWL->{$w} = 1; }
    }
    return 1;
}
1;
